==Information==
*At around 10:44 AM JST, the Rabaul Server (ラバウル基地) has suddenly started having heavy connection issues, which forced the Server to go down for Emergency Maintenance.
*The Server Database was found to have been damaged, which required the Server to be restored back to a previous available data point.
**The Rabaul Server Data was restored up to the July 20th, 04:00 AM JST point.
*The Emergency Maintenance ended at 07:30 AM JST.

===Compensation===
*All Rabaul Server Admirals will receive 1,800 {{Fuel}}{{Ammo}}{{Steel}}{{Bauxite}} as compensation (only up to their respective Automatic Regeneration Value)
**Any Rabaul Server Admirals who were logged in during the time when the Server issue had occurred will receive 3,000 {{Fuel}}{{Ammo}}{{Steel}}{{Bauxite}} (will go above the forementioned Automatic Regeneration Value)
*Any Cash Items purchased from the [[Shop]] lost from the Rollback will be restored based on the Purchase log. 

===Next Scheduled Maintenance may be delayed===
*Due to the incident today, the previously scheduled [[Thread:669186|July 25th Maintenance]] and the Server Transfer into Yokosuka, Maizuru, Kure, and Sasebo may be delayed to August 1st. 

